two weeks to figure out.

00:36:11.740 --> 00:36:16.840
Ticklish is the propensity to be
tickled, so if you are ticklish

00:36:16.840 --> 00:36:20.750
that means you're able to be
tickled but tickly is the magnitude

00:36:20.750 --> 00:36:26.850
of the sensation, just to clarify.

00:36:26.850 --> 00:36:32.680
So, scenario 2 is that the
joystick moves in the one direction

00:36:32.680 --> 00:36:36.010
and then the tickle finger
moves in the same direction

00:36:36.010 --> 00:36:38.460
but after a delay of a few seconds.

00:36:38.460 --> 00:36:41.350
So you move the joystick
up a few seconds as

00:36:41.350 --> 00:36:44.750
