00:36:58.900 --> 00:37:02.420
and that was very tickly, okay?

00:37:02.420 --> 00:37:04.900
So, that's interesting.

00:37:04.900 --> 00:37:09.680
So now we know why we
can't tickle ourselves.

00:37:09.680 --> 00:37:16.210
The reason is when you intend
to tickle yourself, your body,

00:37:16.210 --> 00:37:20.370
