00:37:29.600 --> 00:37:32.470
and then when the actual
sensation I feel when I do,

00:37:32.470 --> 00:37:35.900
when I do that motion
matches the prediction,

00:37:35.900 --> 00:37:37.950
they cancel out the brain sort

00:37:37.950 --> 00:37:41.000
