and makes it not tickly.

00:37:41.000 --> 00:37:47.720 position:56%
Because the nature of being tickled
is that it's an unexpected sensation

00:37:47.720 --> 00:37:50.160
so when you can predict it,
when someone else does it

00:37:50.160 --> 00:37:55.110
to you the brain doesn't nullify
this rather you feel the entire

00:37:55.110 --> 00:37:58.210
sensation and it can
be very exciting.

00:37:58.210 --> 00:38:05.590
And so again it seems like the
